IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.F_SSTWaybillsPerParcel') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.F_SSTWaybillsPerParcel
GO

IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_SSTWaybillsPerParcel') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_SSTWaybillsPerParcel
GO


CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_SSTWaybillsPerParcel (
	[lms_waybillsperparcel_parcelid] int,
    [lms_waybillsperparcel_waybillid] int,
    [lms_waybillsperparcel_loadid] int
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Semi Structured Data/OPS/sstwaybillsperparcel.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.T_SSTWaybillsPerParcel
GO
